@velvet. Yeah, sorry about that. 'Tis my first upload, you see, and I didn't mean to do it twice. I kept getting errors every time from TPB, so I didn't think it had uploaded. Come to find out it had worked twice, but given me errors both times anyway. When I found out there were two of them, I immediately went to delete the other.
